rows.label: bf11590100_0020
rows.name: No, thank you... You saved us.

rows.label: bf11590100_0050
rows.name: It's been 80 years hasn't it, Shin?

rows.label: bf11590100_0070
rows.name:
You and Ornella used to ride on my back.
We used to have a lark, flying about.

rows.label: bf11590100_0090
rows.name: And I suppose she's your Driver now?

rows.label: bf11590100_0100
rows.name:
Laura.
I've been with Shin for 17 years already

rows.label: bf11590100_0120
rows.name: You were fortunate to be picked up by her, Shin

rows.label: bf11590100_0130
rows.name:
Nuncle... We're just in the way here.
Perhaps we should leave it to the soldiers and just go.

rows.label: bf11590100_0142
rows.name: Shall we head for the Iran womb?

rows.label: bf11590100_0150
rows.name: Yes. I'd say we're bound to.

rows.label: bf11590100_0180
rows.name:
Please, go ahead.
We will join you, once we've made a report to the king.
